author: mvila09
title: ''The mission always comes first''-Captain Rex in Star Wars The Clone Wars
review: Hey all,i just got this set today because legocolecter abu-h919 gave it to me.Also this is my first key chain set and i must say i love it because Rex is my fav character in The CW movie.Pros Captain Rex,Mask is very detailed,You can just rip off the chain so you can have Rex as a minifig. Cons I cant really think of any.*****5 stars.

author: asianlego
title: Captain of the Clone Troopers
review:
Captain Rex is now captured.. on a keychain! I just got this set today for MYR 20 (USD 5.70) and the minifig is so cool! Although he is glued together (shame, I really wanted to see how his face looked like!) you can still twist his head round and bend his knees and move his arms. I have placed this on my pencilcase and I intend to play with it during my major examinations next week (after finishing each paper, of course!)

-asianlego
